Type of Feat: Spellcasting
Prerequisite: Heal 8, Turn Undead.
Specifics: You can spend a turn attempt to grant fast healing 3 to all living creatures within a 60-ft. burst. The fast healing lasts for a number of rounds equal to 1 + your Charisma modifier (minimum 1 round).
Use: Selected.
<i>You can channel positive energy to grant nearby living creatures the ability to recover from their wounds quickly.<i>